<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include("../partials/header") %>

        <main class="py-8 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <article class="lg:col-span-2">
                        <div class="bg-white">
                            <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
                                <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
                                <span class="mx-2">></span>
                                <a href="/cleaning" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Cleaning</a>
                                <span class="mx-2">></span>
                                <span class="text-gray-800">Pet-Friendly Cleaning</span>
                            </nav>

                            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
                                Pet-Friendly Cleaning Tips for a Fresh Home
                            </h1>

                            <div class="mb-8">
                                <img src="/images/pet-friendly-cleaning-tips.webp"
                                    alt="Happy pet in a clean home environment"
                                    class="w-full h-80 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg" fetchpriority="high">
                            </div>

                            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                                    Owning a pet brings joy, but it also brings unique cleaning challenges. Maintaining
                                    a clean and fresh-smelling home while keeping your furry friends safe requires the
                                    right approach and pet-safe products.
                                </p>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Managing Pet Hair</h2>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Shedding is part of pet ownership, but it doesn't have to
                                    take over your home.</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                                    <li><strong>Frequent Grooming:</strong> Brush your pets regularly to catch hair
                                        before it lands on your furniture.</li>
                                    <li><strong>The Right Vacuum:</strong> Use a vacuum specifically designed for pet
                                        hair with a HEPA filter.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Rubber Squeegees:</strong> Use a squeegee to pull embedded hair out of
                                        carpets and upholstery.</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Natural Odors and Stain Removal
                                </h2>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Avoid harsh chemicals that can irritate your pets. Natural
                                    solutions are often just as effective.</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                                    <li><strong>Baking Soda:</strong> Sprinkle on carpets before vacuuming to neutralize
                                        odors.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Enzymatic Cleaners:</strong> Use these for accidents to break down
                                        biological messes at the source.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Vinegar Solution:</strong> A mixture of water and vinegar is great for
                                        general cleaning.</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">
                                    With a regular routine and pet-safe cleaning habits, you can enjoy a spotless home
                                    and a happy, healthy pet.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>

                    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
                        <div class="sticky top-8 space-y-6">
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Pet Safety Tip</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Always check the labels of cleaning products for warnings about
                                    pets. Avoid products containing bleach or ammonia in areas where pets dwell.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>
                </div>
            </div>
